<h3 id="purpose" permalink="purpose">Purpose</h3>
<p>This file exists only to tell Node how to start your app when you are not running <code>sails lift</code>.  It is only relevant when you start the server from the command line with <code>npm start</code> (i.e. <code>node app</code>).  In most cases, you can safely ignore this file.</p>
